The code requires Java v1.6.

The code has been tested on Windows, Linux and Mac systems.

To run the code on a Linux system, do:

> tar xvf IGMtransmission.tar    %this untars the file and creates the directory tree

> mkdir output                   % this creates  the subdirectory "output" for containing files output by the code

>java -jar IGMtransmission.jar  %this executes the java GUI

Click on the Help tab for user instructions.

A description of the design and operation of the code is provided in:
doc/IGMtransmission.pdf.

